author: Atomic Shrimp
description:
Here's a coastal walk I have been thinking about for a while now - starting at Lulworth Cove, over the top of Hambury Hill to Durdle Door - and while we're there, a little bit further on to Scratchy Bottom!

https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Scratchy%27s_Bottom

title: A Windswept Walk to Durdle Door and Scratchy Bottom
